  "_comment": "Copy this file to 'secrets.local.json' (which is git-ignored) and fill in real values. Anything here overrides display_config.json, so you can keep passwords/API keys OUT of the main config. Environment variables (SELAH_EMAIL_PASSWORD, SELAH_WEATHER_API_KEY, SELAH_WEB_PASSWORD, SELAH_EMAIL_ADDRESS, SELAH_ERROR_EMAIL) override even these.",
